This paper discusses integrity constraints in databases and their adaptation to reasoning frameworks. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories in computer science, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), logic in computer science (cs.LO), software engineering (cs.SE), and programming languages (cs.PL). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
